    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Add your <strong>butternut squash cubes</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray[s] in the oven for 15-20 min or until tender and golden</p>",
      "order": 1,
