      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped shallot</strong>, <strong>tomato</strong>,<strong> ginger</strong>,<strong> garlic</strong> and your <strong>ground turmeric </strong>to the<strong> food processor</strong> with the seeds</p><p>Add a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong> and blitz until smooth – this is your <strong>spice paste</strong></p><p>Chop your<strong> creamed coconut </strong>roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve your<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong> and <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>creamed</strong> <strong>coconut</strong> in 200ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [260ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[340ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your<strong> coconut stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
