            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, zest <strong>half</strong> your<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>lime[s]</strong>, then cut in half</p><p>Cut your<strong> green chilli[es]</strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop ﬁnely</p><p>Add the<strong> lime zest</strong> and <strong>half</strong> of the<strong> chopped chilli </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) to the <strong>cooked rice </strong>and give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>lime & chilli rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
