            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Squeeze the juice of <strong>half</strong> the <strong>zested</strong> <strong>lime </strong>over the <strong>Keralan-style squash curry</strong> and serve it with the <strong>lime & chilli rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Cut the<strong> remaining zested lime </strong>into 1 wedge per person</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining chopped chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
